c: 4
v: 78
t: "Wherever ye are, death will find you out, even if ye are in towers built up strong and high!\" If some good befalls them, they say, \"This is from Allah\"; but if evil, they say, \"This is from thee\" (O Prophet). Say: \"All things are from Allah.\" But what hath come to these people, that they fail to understand a single fact"